<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-67-0041 </DOCNO><TEXT>Technique for exact determination of charged particle beam position ina space, which is realized by means of its electrostatic modulation andselective detection of current signal from a collector, is described.The merit of this method, besides simplicity of a current transducerand recording instruments, lies in usage of beam modulation which hascertain advantages during work with additional collector radiation load,for example, under conditions of plasma experiments. Possibility forusing the technique for determination of current density distributionin tokamak plasma is discussed.</TEXT></DOC>